---
import '../styles/global.css';
const pageTitle = "Thamara Kandabada - Home";

// src/pages/index.astro
const userAgent = Astro.request.headers.get('user-agent') || '';

if (userAgent.includes('curl')) {
  const terminalText = `
 Thamara Kandabada
 Generalist. Tinkerer.
 
 See what's happening now: https://thamara.co.uk/now
`;

  return new Response(terminalText, {
    headers: {
      'Content-Type': 'text/plain; charset=utf-8',
    },
  });
}
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/tk.png" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} >
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.typekit.net/lbp7mnn.css">
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="banner">
      <p class="banner-text">Work in progress: this is a clone of my WordPress site, currently being built in Astro, for eventual migration. Visit my <a href="https://thamara.co.uk">current site</a> for the latest updates.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/colophon/">Colophon</a>
    <a href="/notebook/">Notebook</a>

    <h1>Greetings, friends & strangers.</h1>

    <p>Welcome to my personal website.</p>
    <p>I’m Thamara, <a href="/resume">furniture-peddler</a> by day and <a href="/now">wearer-of-many-hats</a> by night. Currently based in Belfast, Northern Ireland.</p></p>
    <p>I’ve had a website since 2014, which was when I first learned the basics of web design—specifically, HTML, CSS, and WordPress. This is the fourth or fifth iteration; I’ve now lost count.</p>
    <p>Learn more about how this site is built in <a href="/colophon">the colophon</a>, or explore below.</p>

    <p>Thank you for visiting. Sign my <a href="/guestbook">guestbook</a>.</p>

    <h2>Explore my digital garden</h2>
    
    <h3>At a glance</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/resume">Resume</a></li>
      <li><a href="/now">What I'm up to</a></li>
      <li><a href="/uses">What I'm using</a></li>
      <li><a href="/gigs">Gigs I've been to</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://physicalmedia.thamara.co.uk">Blu-ray collection</a></li>
      <li><a href="/hello">Say hello</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h3>From the notebook</h3>
    <p>Latest posts placeholder</p>

    <h3>See the neighbourhood</h3>
    <p>IndieWeb Webring placeholder</p>

  </body>
</html>
